    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>[In nomine domini Dei eterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21"
                            >Berengarius</persName> divina favente clementia [<rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Notum sit omnibus
                        fideli]bus sancte Dei Aecclesie [nostrisque presentibus et futuris, qualiter
                        ob amorem Dei omnipoten]tis et ob reme[dium anime nostre nostrorumque
                        predecessorum perd]onavimus <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1402"
                            key="#Mother_churches">sancte <placeName ref="#places/505"
                                >Aritine</placeName>
                            <rs key="#Mother_churches">ęcclesię</rs></orgName> in qua [beati Donati
                        martiris] Christi corpus humatum quiescit, cui etiam ęcclesię <persName
                            key="#Bishops #fidelisOf" ref="#people/273">Petrus</persName>,
                        [venerabilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> dilectu]sque <rs
                            key="#fidelisOf">fidelis</rs> noster preesse dignoscitur, quandam <rs
                            key="#Churches">ęcclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >Sancti Marini</orgName> cum suis pertinentiis et <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >[Piun]ta</placeName> c[um omnibus s]uis appenditiis nec non <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Gratigiata</placeName> cum omnibus suis pertinentiis, sicut olim de
                            [<rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/1403">Areti]no</geogName> sub
                        integritate pertinuerunt una cum casis, terris, v[ineis, campis, pratis,]
                        pascuis, silvis, salectis, sacio[nibus], aquis aquarumque decursibus, <rs
                            key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Slave">servis et ancillis</rs>, <rs key="#Aldius">aldionibus
                            et aldianis</rs>, montibus, vallibus, planitiebus seu cum omnibus ad
                        eadem tria loca pertinentibus. Haec omnia <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >de nostro iure et dominio in prefate ecclesie ius et dominium</rs>
                        omnino transfundimus atque donamus ad habendum, tenendum, comutandum et
                        fruendum, [qualib]et ecclesiastica censura amota totius publice partis
                        contraditione aut invasione vel molestia cuiusquam. Si quis igitur hoc
                        nostrum imperiale preceptum infringere vel violare temtaverit, sciat se
                        conpositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras centum</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem camere nostre</rs> et medietatem Petro
                        eiusdem ecclesie episcopo suisque successoribus. Quod ut verius credatur et
                        diligenitus observetur, manu propria roborantes de anulo nostro subter
                        insigniri iussimus. Signum domni (M) Beren[garii piissimi imperatoris.]
                            [<persName key="#Chancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1501"
                            >Iohannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> et] <rs key="#Chancellor"
                            >ca[ncellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName key="#Archchancellor #Bishops"
                            ref="#people/216">Ardingi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi.] Data IIII non. Ian.,
                        anno dominice incarnatio[ni]s DCCCCXVI, domni vero Berengarii piissimi regis
                        XXVIII, imperii autem sui primo, indictione IIII. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/1082">Mucello</placeName>. In Christi nomine feliciter,
                        amen.</ab>
                </div>
